import React from 'react'
import './main.css'
import Main from './pages/Main'
import Home from './pages/Home'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Route>
        <Main />
      </Route>
      <Route>
        <Home />
      </Route>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
